title.en: Denka, Anata ga Suteta Onna ga Honmono no Seijo desu
Honmono no Seijo Janai to Bareta no ni, Outei Denka ni Semararete imasu
Nisemono Seijo ga Honmono ni Katsugi Agerareru made Noso no Katei
Kouhoubu Shussin no Akuyaku Reijou desu ga Muhyoujou na Ouji ni "Kimi wo Te Hanashitakunai" to Iwaremashita
Ouji, Konyaku Haki Shita no wa Sochira na no de, Kowai Kao de Kocchi Niramanaide kudasai.
Saijoukyuu no Seijorashii desu ga, Ryuuou-sama no Hanayome ni wa narimasen! - Tsuihousareta no de Kusushi to shite Daini no Jinsei wo Oukashimasu
Watashi, Seijo. Ima, Kankinsarete Iru no
Nise Seijo da to Ikenie ni Saretara, Maou-sama ni Kyuukonsaremashita
Nise Seijo!? Mira no Boukentan - Tsuihousaremashita ga, Jitsu wa Saikyou na no de Second Life wo Tanoshimimasu!
Iki Okure Seijo no Shiawase - Konyaku Hakisareta to Omottara Mazoku no Ouji-sama ni Dekiaisaretemasu!
Konyaku Hakisareta "Kuuki" na Watashi, Nariagari no Danna-sama ni Totsugimashita.
Kanpeki Sugite Kawaige ga nai to Konyaku Hakisareta Seijo wa Ringoku ni Urareru
Kizuna no Seijou wa Shinjitai - Mukosei no Seijo wa Henkyou no Machi kara Nariagaru
Gimai ga Seijo dakara to Konyakuhaki Saremashita ga, Watashi wa Yousei no Itoshigo desu
Ikenie to shite Surerareta no de, Henkyou Hakke ni Jibun wo Urimasu
